WEBVTT

00:00:18.334 --> 00:00:25.542 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In this world,
it’s hard to find a friend—

00:00:25.542 --> 00:00:32.949 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Someone you can turn to
who’s with you till the end.

00:00:32.949 --> 00:00:39.823 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I used to dream
I’d find a people who could be

00:00:39.823 --> 00:00:50.333 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
More than just some friends
and more like family.

00:00:55.071 --> 00:01:02.345 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My search is over.
I’ve come to know

00:01:02.345 --> 00:01:10.153 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I’ve finally found God’s people;
I feel the love they show.

00:01:10.153 --> 00:01:17.227 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now I live that dream
that meant so much to me.

00:01:17.227 --> 00:01:26.035 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I found more than friends;
I found Jehovah’s family.

00:01:26.069 --> 00:01:36.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now I have brothers;
I have sisters, mothers, fathers too,

00:01:36.412 --> 00:01:43.486 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Little boys and little girls,
older brothers who

00:01:43.486 --> 00:01:52.862 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Come from ev’ry tribe
and race and nationality.

00:01:52.862 --> 00:02:00.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love to be part
of Jehovah’s family.

00:02:02.172 --> 00:02:08.578 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love each other;
our bond is strong.

00:02:08.578 --> 00:02:16.286 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love to have the honor
of knowing we belong

00:02:16.286 --> 00:02:33.469 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To the greatest brotherhood we’ll ever see.
We love to be part of Jehovah’s family.

00:02:49.319 --> 00:03:07.337 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, we come from ev’ry race and nationality.
We love to be part of Jehovah’s family.

00:03:08.371 --> 00:03:15.044 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our God invites us
to be more than a friend.

00:03:15.044 --> 00:03:23.019 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He wants us in his fam’ly;
his love will never end.

00:03:23.019 --> 00:03:29.926 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Just to think
that we will live eternally,

00:03:29.926 --> 00:03:48.611 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then we’ll all be part of Jehovah’s family—
A part of Jehovah’s family,

00:03:52.448 --> 00:04:05.061 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Family,
Family.

